    "WinoGrande (Sakaguchi et al, 2021) adjusts the WSC dataset by redesigning the task in a fill-in-the-blank format.",
    "WinoWhy (Zhang et al, 2020a) extends the WSC dataset by introducing a new task of explaining referential relationships.",
    "The sentiment analysis task, commonly known as emotion classification, seeks to analyze and deduce the emotional inclination of provided texts, commonly categorized as positive, negative, or neutral sentiments.",
    "This task finds practical utility in diverse domains, including social media monitoring, product review analysis, and market research.",
    "Classic sentiment analysis datasets include IMDB (Maas et al, 2011), Sentiment140 (Go et al, 2009), SST-2 (Socher et al, 2013), and EPRSTMT (Xu et al, 2021)."
